title: Venice Beach Muscle Beach
name: Original Muscle Beach
address: 1800 Ocean Front Walk, Venice, CA 90291, USA

details.description: The legendary Muscle Beach in Venice, California. This iconic outdoor gym has been the birthplace of the modern fitness culture and attracts athletes from around the world. Features comprehensive equipment for all calisthenics movements.
Modern outdoor workout area in the heart of Moscow's famous Gorky Park. Well-maintained equipment suitable for all skill levels. Very popular spot among local street workout community.

title: Parc de la Ciutadella Workout Area
name: Ciutadella Park Bars

details.description: Beautiful outdoor workout spot in Barcelona's largest park. Located near the lake with great atmosphere. Equipment is well-maintained and suitable for various exercises.
Outdoor gym equipment on the scenic Primrose Hill in London. Great views of the city skyline. Basic but solid equipment for fundamental calisthenics movements.
Massive outdoor workout area on the grounds of the former Tempelhof Airport. One of the largest calisthenics parks in Europe with extensive equipment. Perfect for all skill levels.

title: Central Park Great Lawn Exercise Area
name: Central Park Calisthenics
address: Central Park, Mid-Park at 79th St, New York, NY 10024, USA

details.description: Popular workout spot in the heart of Manhattan. Located near the Great Lawn with plenty of space for training. Gets busy during peak hours but worth the visit.

title: Bondi Beach Outdoor Gym
name: Bondi Beach Fitness Park
address: Queen Elizabeth Drive, Bondi Beach NSW 2026, Australia

details.description: Iconic beachside workout spot with ocean views. Train with the sound of waves in the background. Very popular with locals and tourists alike. Best visited early morning or late afternoon.
Peaceful workout area in one of Tokyo's largest parks. Clean and well-maintained equipment. Great atmosphere with respectful training community.
